<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.3">
<l>niṉṟa māmaru tiṟṟu vīḻana ṭanta niṉmalaṉ nēmiyāṉ</l>
<l>eṉṟum vāṉavark kaito ḻumiṇait tāma</l>
<l>raiyaṭi yempirāṉ</l>
<l>kaṉṟi māripo ḻinti ṭakkaṭi tāni raikkiṭar nīkkuvāṉ</l>
<l>ceṉṟu kuṉṟame ṭutta vaṉtiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam of the one who lifted the mountain,</l>
<l>Going to quickly end the suffering for the cow herd</l>
<l rend="indent">when the hard rain pelted down,</l>
<l>Our lord whose feet, a pair of lotuses, celestials ever worship,</l>
<l rend="indent">hands [joined], calling,</l>
<l>“Discus bearer, unblemished one who walked,</l>
<l rend="indent">so the great standing marutu [trees] broke and fell.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
